{"tid":1888414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TG黃channel食人血饅頭賣炒價口罩仲惡過李政熙","createTime":"2020-02-20T07:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T17:50:09.000Z","uid":121831,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f81162bc79616ca0f08dcfaa0bb3ecdc31df7e65","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"事緣有個channel叫「不專業公民教育」<br />\n都有成7千幾subscriber<br />\n今日講話佢地有口罩賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/754Yknp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F754Yknp.png&h=f944d675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成四百幾蚊盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有太多人齋問唔買啦<br />\nAdmin嬲嬲豬了<br />\n你地識口罩條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7Qc9gb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7Qc9gb.png&h=15c610b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>爆房錢就俾得起<br />\n買我啲口罩就俾唔起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"84d650568b63915d9c789aefd5e8eb42c9b67318","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8864ac5b681fa1612fe5a141ec0defc467a7bdb9","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:43:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"653671305d1957252b9f25fd92f3b8f6238864a0","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2b564ed0915d219533a2053e434adfcab2d967e6","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"66024f0b943c878d7bdac9b5a1c0c0b7c0340f00","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dfe4207905db8ca4278ad0906ddc5f4e2039bc97","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"ebe8db4de2b694742f17b8484f543289b9a0c6a8","tid":1888414,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"有錢就要比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e40c5d7f2da428770b64a1a98c7f487d219413","tid":1888414,"uid":236414,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"做咩唔cap埋呢段上黎？人地有explain埋點解supply會越來越少。<br />\n「小童用口罩基本當地攞貨價係HKD4.5一個，若要Fedex 1星期內到，連運費要HKD8一個。」<br />\n7蚊一個真外科口罩唔覺得過分，唔好開口埋口話人食人血饅頭咁口臭，不學無術既兒登仔。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nBy 不專業公民教育 @wearenotrioters<br />\n<br />\n尋晚同賣家們嘅電話會議（文字版）<br />\n<br />\n一、有關美軍大量採購口罩<br />\n<br />\n1. 美國政府一直都有相應指引囤貨。<br />\n2. 囤貨嘅地方有好多，分佈各州各市，例如各大零售商嘅倉庫、軍營等。<br />\n3. 當啲貨就嚟過期會release返畀民用／緊急醫療用。<br />\n4. 但今次，美軍比起之前伊波拉、禽流感動用更大規模嘅採購。<br />\n5. 喱次採購令本身已經相當緊絀嘅零售供應幾乎完全截斷。<br />\n6. 美軍今次供應口罩係去本地軍營、外地駐軍同海外艦隊。<br />\n<br />\n二、貨源、供應、銷售問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 有品質嘅口罩，非常缺；劣質口罩充斥市場；消費者唔識分辨好壞。<br />\n2. 唔建議喺東南亞source口罩，因為口罩佢3層構造係有特定要求。<br />\n3. 建議係買返平時醫院、診所、牙醫等會用到嘅牌子。<br />\n4. 非中國生產商（除台灣、日本、韓國，因為佢地要內部生產以供國民所需），喺EXW嘅貨價炒高平均7倍，最高16倍。<br />\n5. 小童用口罩基本當地攞貨價係HKD4.5一個，若要Fedex 1星期內到，連運費要HKD8一個。<br />\n6. 中國以外嘅國家，就算受到疫情波及，但本土工業產能無受影響。<br />\n7. 置生產線唔難，但要有齊cert等同其他立立雜雜就要半年先可以生產。<br />\n8. 就算生產到都係以供本地用為先。<br />\n9. 意味住未來半年仍然全球短缺有品質嘅口罩。<br />\n10. 原材料以往一直依賴中國供應，今次冇咗主要供應地變相基本成本，尤其加埋外國人工成本，口罩就算喺半年後生產到大批，都唔會係未有疫症時期嘅價錢，可以預計為原先EXW嘅5倍內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上嘅對話來源係我同三位Antiviral Mask嘅大手賣家同兩個medical supplier嘅聯絡而得。<br />\n<br />\n曲：不過美國佬都係狼子野心想搞亂我哋大中華嘅和平穩定繁榮，完全信唔過。<br />\n<br />\n直：仲覺得幾舊水一盒口罩貴嘅自求多福。"},{"pid":"272855798b7ba5a32b0611a0ad4af2b9a8318df3","tid":1888414,"uid":296677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"其他嘢唔見人追得咁足<br />\n咁唔滿意咪返去問政府攞啦"},{"pid":"1346207e93a4b5f8b6afc1f8b3029c90cf0d00a0","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"爆房幾舊水畀得起<br />\n買幾舊水口罩就畀唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a538655ed81f4dc142e6d1f22530aacbd796c78","tid":1888414,"uid":36813,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"如果係有規格 好少少質素既口罩<br />\n真係要呢個價<br />\n除非又直接識廠既人 唔使搵代理<br />\n而且可以等 唔係急用 <br />\n先話平少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你用印尼口罩個價去同人比係無得比架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我買左德國口罩4盒自用 圍起條數都要200 幾蚊一盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db09b2f5cbda23867b5b4ba6f2701639c8f9cf5b","tid":1888414,"uid":135274,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"商家佬賣N95俾醫管局，15蚊一個，醫管局話要用疫症前既價錢買，就話醫管局官僚，唔知而家個價升成點，唔識搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nASTM Level 2，普通醫護都未必用到，430蚊賣俾你就話人血饅頭，你贏"},{"pid":"ad3e43dd1bc5a3fb4b21e024092e9bf8e460a007","tid":1888414,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"口罩7-8蚊個就覺得貴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人根本唔缺口罩</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"456156bbe4ea1f78235ef18e967062809d343663","tid":1888414,"uid":98958,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"